{
  "stem": "9943.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And they didn't have enough positions for Russians then to-- to replace doctors in-- some-- in a hospital or in a clinic, because so many have come from all of Ukraine from-- and from Moscow and from wherever you want.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I am near the train, looking to see whether I'll find someone from my area, maybe my husband would come, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "People did find themselves, sometimes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Each one was going somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in [NON-ENGLISH], which is the health-- the health section of the ministry, they decided that they are going to send 50 doctors from those refugees to villages, kolhoz collective arms.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know about the kolhoz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I signed up on this list.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put a list in the wall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who wants to go to kolhoz?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I signed up the second one, that list that I want to go to kolhoz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I didn't have, as a matter of fact, any choice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was interviewed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What-- the man that interviewed me, [INAUDIBLE] said what kind of a kolhoz I want.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, I want one that is near a station-- near a train station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So said he to me, was Kaganovich a good-- a good man?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I don't have any reason to think that he was not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kaganovich was one of Stalin's helpers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said, I'll send you to the kolhoz in the name of Kaganovich, which is near the station [INAUDIBLE], because I'm ask-- I asked him for near the station.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- so he gave me this-- that assignment, and I met-- and we-- we could take with us a nurse.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I met around the station somewhere, a young woman who was from the area that I come from, in Volhynia [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
